	ASK_THE_PC:
 Ask the pc is a bootable little application made to make your life easier. 
Do you have a to make a though choice? Let smile man make the decision for you. 
All you have to do it boot it up and press a button. After that, smile man will decide it for you.
Smile man can bring you three different answers, its either yes (Y), no (N) or undecided (?). Smile man will emote accordingly.

	0      0	0      0	  0      0	
      XX        XX	
	XXXXXXXX      XXXXXXXXXXXX	  XXXXXXXX	
     					XX	  XX
     Y		     ?  		N
  If you have another question, feel free to press any button again!
